# Name: Clearlooks-solarized
# Author: John McKnight <jmcknight@gmail.com>
# Color modified by Kenji Rikitake <kenji.rikitake@acm.org>
# based on the solarized dark color theme available at 
# <http://ethanschoonover.com/solarized>
# Note: This is a port of the Clearlooks-Olive metacity theme to Openbox.

